quran[665]{c,v,t}:
  10,1,"AlĂŽ, wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt tuĂ»wibt"
  10,2,"Day d lwehma, i medden, ma NweĂȘĂȘa n i urgaz nnsen: \"nabi imdanen, becceĂŽ wid iumnen ar ad afen arraz umĂąin ar Mass nnsen\"? Nnan ijehliyen: \"wagi, s tidep, d aseĂȘĂȘar n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  10,3,"Ih, Mass nnwen d Ăebbi, i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, IĂąannec $ef usgeld, Iseyyi lameĂŽ. Ur illi umcafaĂą siwa ma IĂąammed as. D wagi ay d Ăebbi, Mass nnwen. Ihi, Ăąabdet eP. Day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  10,4,"ÂŁuĂŽeS akw tu$alin nnwen. LemĂąahda n Ăebbi d tidep. Ih, Inezzu axlaq, Ippales, iwakken ad Ikafi wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, s lmizan. I wid ijehlen, tissit iĂŽ$an, aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan, imi llan jehlen"
  10,5,"D Neppa i Irran iĂźij d lefnaĂŽ, aggur d tafat. Iwezn as tiswaĂąin, iwakken a ppissinem amvan iseggwasen, akked leĂȘsab. Ur Ixliq Ăebbi ayagi, siwa s tidep. IpfeĂ»Ă»il issekniyen i ugdud issnen"
  10,6,"S tidep, di lemgarda ger yiv akked wass, akked wayen Ixleq Ăebbi di tmurt akked igenwan, ard issekniyen i ugdud i ipĂȘezziben"
  10,7,"Ih, wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidneÂŁ, i tqennaĂą tmeddurt di ddunit, u rekden degs, d wid i istehzan $ef issekniyen nneÂŁ"
  10,8,"Wigi, axxam nnsen di tmes, ilmend n wayen keppben"
  10,9,"Ih, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Inhu Mass nnsen, s liman nnsen. Ad ppazzalen isaffen seddawat sen, di leonanat isaĂądiyen"
  10,10,"Anuju nnsen degs: \"gedha s yissek a Ăebbi\"! Azul nnsen d: \"tifrat\". Anuju nnsen aneggaru: \"ccekĂŽan i Ăebbi, Mass imavalen"
  10,11,"Lemmer ad IaĂąoel Ăebbi cceĂŽĂŽ ar imdanen, akken nitni ĂȘaren $ef lxiĂŽ, yili ibbwev asen lajel nnsen. A Nanef i wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidneÂŁ, ad ddebdben di lbe$wv nnsen"
  10,12,"Amdan, ma iĂȘuza t ccqa, ad aÂŁ ÂŁ d isiwel, iĂ©Ă©el, iqqim ne$ ibedd. Mi s Nekkes ccqa s, ad iteddu amzun ur d inuj $uĂŽneÂŁilmend n ccqa i t iĂȘuzan. Akka ay ppucebĂȘen igiten nnsen i imaĂąfan"
  10,13,"Ni$ Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnwen, imi densen. Ussan d $uĂŽsen imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, ur llin d wid ara iamnen. Akka ay NepqeĂźĂźi agdud ibe$wviyen"
  10,14,"Sinna, Nerra kwen d igensas di tmurt, deffir sen, a Nwali amek ara txedmem"
  10,15,"Ma $ĂŽan asen issekniyen nneÂŁ iberrzen, wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidneÂŁ, ad inin: \"awi d LeqwĂŽan nniven, ne$ beddel it\". Ini: \"ur felli a t beddle$, s leb$i n yiman iw. Teddu$ kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweĂȘĂȘan. Nek ugade$, ma xedĂąa$ Mass iw, aĂąaqeb n wass ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
  10,16,"Ini: \"lemmer i S ihwi i Ăebbi, ur awen t id mli$, ur awen t id mmekti$. Ni$ zed$e$ yidwen tameddurt, uqbel is. Day ur tfehmem ara"
  10,17,"Anwa i idensen kteĂŽ, ger win id igren tikerkas $ef Ăebbi, ne$ win inekĂŽen issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebĂȘen ibe$wviyen"
  10,18,"La Ăąabden, war Ăebbi, ayen ur ten neĂźĂźuĂŽu, ur ten nenfaĂą. La qqaĂŽen: \"wigi d imcafĂąen nne$ ar Ăebbi\". Ini: \"day a pxebbĂŽem Ăebbi $ef wayen ur Issin, di tmurt akked igenwan\"? Gedha s yiS! I AĂąlay sennig wayen pcaraken"
  10,19,"Llan imdanen d yiwen n lois kan. Sinna, mgaraden. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, s$uĂŽ Mass ik, ad yili uĂȘuddu, garasen, $ef wayen i$ef mgaraden"
  10,20,"La qqaĂŽen: \"a lemmer id irs $uĂŽes ussekni n Mass is\"! Ini: \"tabavnit ar Ăebbi kan. Ihi, gganit. Nek, yidwen, seg wid iggunin"
  10,21,"Ma NesĂȘess i imdanen aĂȘunu, deffir twa$it i ten iĂȘuzan, atnan la ppandin i issekniyen nneÂŁ. Ini: \"Ăebbi Yif akw akken Ip$awal di tiĂȘeĂŽci\". Imersulen nneÂŁ, s tidep, pparun ayen teppandim"
  10,22,"Neppa i kwen Ippawin di lberr, di yill. Alamma, mi tellam di lembwabeĂŽ, teppedum degsen s wavu uĂ»wib, feĂŽĂȘen yis, tusa d tbucivant $uĂŽsen, ppasent ed lemwao $uĂŽsen, si yal tama, ĂȘulfan a d tezzi fellasen. NaĂąĂŽen Ăebbi, s lqaĂąida i Neppa: \"ma Tsellkev a$ si tagi, ar a nili seg wid isnemmiren"
  10,23,"Mi ten Isellek, imiren u$alen be$wven di tmurt, war ssebba. A yimdanen! Lbe$wv nnwen, siwa $ef yiman nnwen. Zzhu di tmeddurt n ddunit, sinna, $uĂŽneÂŁ tu$alin nnwen, ad awen Nmel ayen txeddmem"
  10,24,"Amedya n tmeddurt di ddunit, am aman kan. Nesse$li ten id seg igenni, xelven akked im$an n tmurt, iseg teppen imdanen akked lmal. Mi tcebbeĂȘ tmurt, tu$al d tuzyint, $ilen, imezda$ is, ar deg ufus nnsen ay tella. Iusa p id lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, deg iv, ne$ deg wass, Nerra p d ahicuĂŽ, amzun ur teoouoeg ass izeryen. Akka ay NfeĂ»Ă»el issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen"
  10,25,"Inecced Ăebbi s axxam n tifrat. Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim"
  10,26,"I wid iweqmen, lewqama, ternuv as. Udmawen nnsen, ur ten ipnal bufsus, ne$ ddell. Widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs ad wekkĂŽen"
  10,27,"AqeĂźĂźi n wid id ibbwin tucmitin, d tucmip itent icban. Ad ndellen. Ur sĂąun amenĂȘul ar Ăebbi. Amzun $ummen wudmawen nnsen, s ccevyat n yiv iberkanen. Widak d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkĂŽen"
  10,28,"Ass ideg ara ten Nfesser akw, a Nini, imiren, i wid icurken: \"imukan nnwen, kunwi akked icriken nnwen\"! Sinna NessemfaĂŽaq iten. A d inin, icriken nnsen: \"maĂ§Ă§i d nekwni ay tĂąabdem"
  10,29,"Ad Iqadd Ăebbi, d Anagi garane$ yidwen, ar ur d necliĂą deg uĂąbbed nnwen"
  10,30,"Din, yal amdan ad iwali ayen iwasa. Ad u$alen ar Ăebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen"
  10,31,"Ini: \"anwa ikwen Ip$itin seg igenni akked tmurt? Anwa ay d Bab n tmejjin akked yiĂ©ĂŽi? Anwa id Issuffu$en amuddir si lmegget, id Issuffu$en lmegget seg umuddir? Anwa i Iseyyin lameĂŽ\"? A d inin: \"d Ăebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, day ur tepĂȘezzibem ara"
  10,32,"D wagi ay d Ăebbi, Mass nnwen n tidep. Deffir tidep, acu i illan, siwa ttelfan? Ihi, acimi texdĂąam"
  10,33,"Akka i iĂ»aĂŽ wawal n Mass ik, $ef wid ixedmen tucmitin. Ih, nitni ur ppamnen"
  10,34,"Ini: \"day illa ger icriken nnwen, win id inzan lxelq, sinna, iules as d\"? Ini: \"Ăebbi inezzu lxelq, sinna, Ippales as d. Ihi, amek ara twexxĂŽem"
  10,35,"Ini: \"day illa, ger icriken nnwen, win i inehhun ar tidep\"? Ini: \"Ăebbi Inehhu ar tidep. Win Inehhun ar tidep, day ur Yif ara, akken Iklal tikli yideS, win ur nennehhu, siwa ma ipwanha? Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepseyyim"
  10,36,"Tegwti, segsen, teddun kan d nnwaya. Nnwaya, war ccekk, ur tebbwi acemma si tidep. Ih, Ăebbi Issen acu xeddmen"
  10,37,"LeqwĂŽan agi ur d innulfa ara, war Ăebbi. Maca, d atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d afeĂ»Ă»el n Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, s$uĂŽ Mass imavalen"
  10,38,"Ne$ la qqaĂŽen: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"awit ed tasuĂŽep i t icban, neccdet seg wanda tzemrem, war Ăebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  10,39,"XaĂźi, skaddben ayen ur nekcim di tmusni nnsen, ur ten id iusi usefhem is. Akka ay skaddben, wid i ten id izwaren. Wali, ihi, amek tevĂŽa d imednas"
  10,40,"Garasen, wid iumnen yis; garasen, wid ur numin yis. Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen ifessaden"
  10,41,"Ma skaddben k, ini: \"i nek igiten iw, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppkam deg wayen xedme$, ur ppka$ deg wayen txedmem"
  10,42,"Garasen, llan wid i k issemĂȘasen. Day tzemrev a pperrev ad slen iĂąeĂ©Ă©ugen, ma llan ur fehhmen"
  10,43,"Garasen, llan wid i k ipmuqulen. Day tzemrev a ppenhuv ider$alen, ma llan ur pwalin"
  10,44,"Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Iddennis imdanen, s wacemma, maca imdanen densen iman nnsen"
  10,45,"Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, amzun sĂąaddan kan saĂąa n wass, ad msaĂąqalen. Ni$ xesĂŽen wid iskaddben timlilit d Ăebbi. Ur pwanhan"
  10,46,"Ad ak Nessken kra seg wayen i sen NĂąahed, ne$ a k id Nawi $uĂŽneÂŁ. Ihi, $uĂŽneÂŁ tu$alin nnsen. Sinna, Ăebbi d Anagi n wayen xeddmen"
  10,47,"I yal lois, amazan. Ma iusa d umazan nnsen, a ppefru garasen s lmizan, ur pwadensen"
  10,48,"QqaĂŽen: \"melmi lemĂąahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  10,49,"Ini: \"ur mlike$ i iman iw vveĂŽĂŽ, ne$ aba$uĂŽ, siwa ayen Ib$a Ăebbi. Yal lois s lajel is\". Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiĂŽen s saĂąa, ur t id sseqĂŽaben"
  10,50,"Ini: \"acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uĂąaqeb iS, deg iv, ne$ deg wass? Acimi ĂȘaren $uĂŽeS ibe$wviyen"
  10,51,"D$a, ma iusa d, a ppamnem yis? Tura, aql akwen t$eĂ»bem fellas"
  10,52,"Sinna, ad asen inin i wid idensen: \"jeĂŽĂŽbet aĂąaqeb n lebda. Ma teppuqeĂźĂźan siwa kan $ef wayen tkeppbem"
  10,53,"Steqsayen k: \"d tidep ayagi\"? Ini: \"ih, s Mass iw, ar ayagi d tidep! Kunwi ur tezmirem i usfunneg"
  10,54,"Xas ad isĂąu, yal amdan idensen, i illan di tmurt, ur d ifeddu yis. Ffren nndama mi walan aĂąaqeb. AĂȘuddu garasen, s lmizan, ur pwadensen"
  10,55,"Day, s tidep, maĂ§Ă§i n Ăebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ih, day lemĂąahda n Ăebbi maĂ§Ă§i d tidep? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen"
  10,56,"Neppa Issidir, Ineqq. ÂŁuĂŽeS ara tu$alem"
  10,57,"A yimdanen! Ni$ iusa kwen id unabi s$uĂŽ Mass nnwen, akked ccfa n wayen iblan ulawen, akked nnhaya, akked uĂȘunu i lmumnin"
  10,58,"Ini: \"s lfevl n Ăebbi akked uĂȘunu S, s waya, xas ad feĂŽĂȘen\". Yif ayen pkemmimen"
  10,59,"Ini: \"twalam ayen i wen d Issers Ăebbi n ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q? Terram segs leĂȘlal d leĂȘĂŽam\". Ini: \"IĂąammed awen Ăebbi, ne$ tesnulfam d $ef Ăebbi"
  10,60,"Acu ara meyyzen, ass n tnekra, wid id igren tikerkas $ef Ăebbi? Ih, Ăebbi d Bab n lfevl af imdanen, maca tegwti segsen ur snemmiren"
  10,61,"Ur teppiliv di liĂȘala, ur temmalev si LeqwĂŽan, ur tepce$wilem di kra, mebla ma Nella d Inagan nnwen, mara tweqmem. Lmizan ubelkim di tmurt u deg igenni, ur idrig i Mass ik. Akken seddaw waya, ne$ sennig es. Akw, di Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  10,62,"Ih, s tidep, iĂȘbiben n Ăebbi ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  10,63,Wid iumnen u llan ĂȘezzben
  10,64,"a ten beccĂŽen s lxiĂŽ di tmeddurt n ddunit, di laxeĂŽt. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawalen n Ăebbi. D wagi ay d rrbeĂȘ ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
  10,65,"Ur k i$webbel wawal nnsen. Ih, tazmert akw n Ăebbi. Neppa Isell, d Amusnaw"
  10,66,"S tidep, day maĂ§Ă§i n Ăebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt? D acu ĂźĂźafaĂŽen wid ipnujun, war Ăebbi, ar icriken? ĂĂźafaĂŽen kan nnwaya. OaĂąĂąlen kan"
  10,67,"Neppa, i wen Irran iv i ureyyeĂȘ nnwen, ass iwakken a pwalim. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud isellen"
  10,68,"Nnan: \"Ăebbi IsĂąa aqcic. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d AmeĂŽkanti. IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ur tesĂąim adabu $ef waya. Day a d tinim $ef Ăebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  10,69,"Ini: \"s tidep, wid id igren tikerkas $ef Ăebbi, ur rebĂȘen"
  10,70,"Zzhu di ddunit, sinna, $uĂŽneÂŁ tu$alin nnsen. D$a, ad asen NsĂąaddi aĂąaqeb uqsiĂȘ, imi llan jehlen"
  10,71,"EĂȘku yasen d tadyant n NuĂȘ, mi inna i ugdud is: \"a yagdud iw! Ma Ă©Ă©ayit fellawen tilin iw, akked usmekti w n issekniyen n Ăebbi, $ef Ăebbi ppekle$, ihi, zduklet lameĂŽ nnwen akked icriken nnwen. Sinna, ur awen teppili lhejna $ef lameĂŽ nnwen, d$a, frut ep felli, ur iyi sganit"
  10,72,"Ma twexxĂŽem, ur awen ssuture$ taqdiĂąt. Ih, taqdiĂąt iw ar Ăebbi kan. Felli lameĂŽ ad ili$ seg imvuĂąen"
  10,73,"Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuĂŽ. Nerra ten d igensas. Ne$meq wid iskaddben issekniyen nneÂŁ. Wali amek tevĂŽa d wid ippunedĂŽen"
  10,74,"Sinna, deffir es, Nuzen ed imazanen ar igduden nnsen. Usan ten id s ubeggen. Ur ssawven ad amnen $ef wayen nekĂŽen zik. Akka ay Nselle$ ulawen ixabiten"
  10,75,"Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa akked HaĂŽun, ar FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is, s issekniyen nneÂŁ. Sme$wĂŽen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibe$wviyen"
  10,76,"Mi ten id tusa tidep, s$uĂŽneÂŁ, nnan: \"wagi, ih, d ssĂȘur n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  10,77,"Inna Musa: \"day a tinim d ssĂȘur wagi, i tidep mi kwen id tusa\"? Ur rebĂȘen iseĂȘĂȘaren"
  10,78,"Nnan: \"day d tusiv $uĂŽne$, ad a$ tesĂźixxĂŽev seg wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne$, a ppu$alem, di sin, d imeqwĂŽanen di tmurt? Ur numin, nekwni, yiswen"
  10,79,"Inna FerĂąun: \"awit iyi d yal aseĂȘĂȘar amusnaw"
  10,80,"Mi d usan iseĂȘĂȘaren, inna yasen Musa: \"veggĂŽet ara tveggĂŽem"
  10,81,"Mi veggĂŽen, inna Musa: \"ayen d tebbwim d ssĂȘur. S tidep, a t Inqev Ăebbi\". Ih, Ăebbi ur Issewqam ara igiten ifessaden"
  10,82,"Ăebbi Itebbit tidep, s wawal iS, xas ugin ibe$wviyen"
  10,83,"I iumnen s Musa, siwa tarwa seg ugdud is, ilmend n tugdi uhewwel n FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is. Ih, FerĂąun d abe$wvi di tmurt. Neppa, s tidep, seg imaĂąfan"
  10,84,"Inna Musa: \"a yagdud iw! Ma teppamnem s Ăebbi, ppeklet fellaS ma d imvuĂąen ay tellam"
  10,85,"Nnan: \"neppkel $ef Ăebbi. A Mass nne$, ur a$ ppara d ahewwel i ugdud imednas"
  10,86,"Sellek a$, s uĂȘunu K, seg ugdud ijehliyen"
  10,87,"NweĂȘĂȘa i Musa akked gma s: \"ebnut ixxamen i ugdud nnwen di MaĂ»eĂŽ, erret ixxamen nnwen ar lqibla, beddet i tĂ©allit. BecceĂŽ lmumnin"
  10,88,"Inna Musa: \"a Mass nne$! S tidep, Tefkiv i FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is, ĂŽĂŽĂȘuĂȘ akked wayla di tmeddurt n ddunit, a Mass nne$, iwakken ad nnetlafen seg ubrid iK. A Mass nne$, Squcc ayla nnsen, S$eĂŽ ulawen nnsen, ur ppamnen alamma walan aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  10,89,"Inna: \"ih, tepwaqbel tnaĂąĂŽit nnwen. Ddut di lewqam, ur teddut d ubrid n wid ur nessin"
  10,90,"Nezzger At IsĂŽail di yill. VefĂŽen ten FerĂąun akked iĂąsekĂŽiwen is, s leb$wev d lewĂąaĂŽa. Armi ibbwev ad i$meq, inna: \"umne$! Ih, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Win is umnen At IsĂŽail. Nek seg imvuĂąen"
  10,91,"Tura! Ni$ zik taĂąĂ»av, telliv seg ifessaden"
  10,92,"Assa, a Nsellek loeppa k, a d tegwri d assekni i wid ara k id ineĂ»fen. AĂźas n medden, s tidep, stehzan deg issekniyen nneÂŁ"
  10,93,"Ni$ Nessers At IsĂŽail deg umkan umĂąin, u N$at iten s wayen ilhan. Ur mgaraden armi ten id tusa tussna. Ih, Mass ik ad IĂȘudd garasen, ass n tnekra, ilmend n wayen i$ef llan mgaraden"
  10,94,"Ma tcukkev $ef wayen i k ed Nessers, steqsi wid i iqqaĂŽen Tazmamt, uqbel ik. Ni$ tusa k id tidep, s$uĂŽ Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun"
  10,95,"Ur ppili seg wid i iskaddben issekniyen n Ăebbi, a ppiliv seg imexsuĂŽen"
  10,96,"Ih, wid i$ef iĂ»aĂŽ Wawal n Mass ik, ur ppamnen"
  10,97,"xas usan ten id akw issekniyen, alamma walan aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  10,98,"A lemmer telli temdint iumnen, u infaĂą p liman is, siwa agdud n Yunes! Mi umnen, NveĂŽĂŽef segsen aĂąaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Neooa ten zzhan tallit kan"
  10,99,"Ma ihwa yaS i Mass ik, ad amnen wid illan di ddunit, akken ma llan. Day a pĂȘeppmev, keĂ§Ă§, i imdanen ad amnen"
  10,100,Ur ippamen umdan siwa ma Irad Ăebbi. Isdullu wid ur nfehhem ara
  10,101,"Ini: \"walit i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ula iwumi issekniyen akked ineddiĂŽen, i ugdud ur neppamen"
  10,102,"Day a pganin kan amedya n wussan n wid i ten id izwaren? Ini: \"gganit, nek yidwen, seg wid ipganin"
  10,103,"Sinna, a Nsellek imazanen nneÂŁ, akked wid iumnen. Akka ay d lwajeb fellaÂŁ, a Nsellek lmumnin"
  10,104,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Ma tcukkem di ddin iw, nek ur Ăąabde$ wid tĂąabdem, war Ăebbi. Maca, Ăąabde$ Ăebbi ara Idmen leĂŽwaĂȘ nnwen. PwamĂŽe$ ad ili$ si lmumnin"
  10,105,"Sbedd udem ik i ddin, s umili ar tidep, ur ppili seg imcurak"
  10,106,"Ur pnuju, war Ăebbi, ar wayen ur k inefĂąan, ur k iĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽun. Ma txedmev akken, keĂ§Ă§, imiren, a ppiliv seg imednas"
  10,107,"Ma IsĂąadda fellak Ăebbi ccqa, ur ak illi ujebbaĂŽ siwa Neppa. Ma Irad ak lxiĂŽ, ur illi usebĂźĂźel i lfevl iS. Ippak it i win i S ihwan, deg ixdimen iS. Neppa IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  10,108,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Ni$ tusa kwen id tidep s$uĂŽ Mass nnwen! Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is; win innetlafen, innetlef kan i iman is. Ur lli$, nek, d awkil nnwen"
