  11,61,"I Tamud, gmat sen ĂĂŒĂaliĂȘ, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ăabdet Ăebbi! Ur tesĂąim ĂŽebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde$ ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaĂȘ, sinna, steĂŽoĂąet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, IqeĂŽb ed, Ippara d awal"
