  11,94,"Mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, Nsellek CuĂąayeb akked wid iumnen yides, s uĂȘunu s$uĂŽneÂŁ. Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
