  11,98,"Ad izwir i ugdud is, ass n tnekra, a ten inheĂŽ ar usario n tmes. A yasario ucmit u$uĂŽ pwanehĂŽen"
  11,99,"A ten ivfeĂŽ xezzu di tagi, u deg wass n tnekra. A tikci tucmip ippunefken"
  11,100,"Ayagi, si teqĂ»ivin n temdinin, i k d Nessawal. Garasent tid ibedden, tid ipwamegren"
  11,101,"Ur ten Nednis. Maca, densen iman nnsen. Ur ten nefĂąan s wacemma, iĂŽebbiten nnsen i la naĂąĂŽen, war Ăebbi, mi d iusa lameĂŽ n Mass ik. I sen rnan, siwa ssxev"
  11,102,"Akka tiyta n Mass ik. Mi Iwwet timdinin i idensen, s tidep, tiyta S teqĂŽeĂȘ, teqseĂȘ"
  11,103,"Ih, deg waya, assekni i wid iugaden aĂąaqeb n laxeĂŽt. Ass nni, d ass unejmaĂą n yimdanen. Ass nni, d ass n ccada"
  11,104,A t NeswexxeĂŽ kan ar lajel iuran
  11,105,"Ass ideg ara d ias, ur d ipmeslay yiwen, siwa ma s tesriĂȘ iS. Ad ilin igeswaĂȘen, isaĂądiyen"
  11,106,"Wanag igeswaĂȘen ad ilin di tmes, s unazaĂą d imeĂźĂźi"
  11,107,"ad wekkĂŽen dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. Ih, Mass ik Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan"
  11,108,"Wanag isaĂądiyen, di Loennet, ad wekkĂŽen, dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. D tikci n war tilas"
  11,109,"Ur k ikeĂ§Ă§em ccekk $ef wayen Ăąabden widak. Ayen Ăąabden am wayen Ăąabden imezwura nnsen, zik. War ccekk, ad asen Nefk amur nnsen, ur inqis"
  11,110,"Ni$, s tidep, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uĂŽ Mass ik, yili useyyi garasen. Haaten, ih, di ccekk imcebbwel fellas"
  11,111,"War ccekk, akken ma llan, ad Ikafi Mass ik igiten nnsen, s lmizan. Neppa, s tidep, Issen ayen xeddmen"
  11,112,"Ihi, ili d uwqim, akken i k ippunefk lameĂŽ, keĂ§Ă§ akked wid isteĂŽoĂąen yidek. Ur be$wvet. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ay txeddmem"
  11,113,"Ur pqeĂŽĂŽibet ar wid idensen, a kwen tnal tmes! Ur tesĂąim bab, war Ăebbi, ihi, ur tepwasellkem"
  11,114,"ĂšĂ©al Ă»beĂȘ, tameddit, kra n lewqat n yiv. S tidep, ise$iyen neqqven tucmitin. Ayagi d asmekti i wid ismektayen"
  11,115,"EĂ»beĂŽ! Ăebbi, s tidep, ur IveggiĂą taqdiĂąt n lĂąuĂ»am"
  11,116,"A lemmer llan, di tsuta i kwen id izwaren, imezgiyen ineqqven asefsed di tmurt! Qlilit kan seg wid Nsellek segsen. Wid idensen ddan akked wayen i ten izhan, u$alen d ibe$wviyen"
  11,117,"Ur Isquccu ara Mass ik timdinin, d aĂȘerfi, ma llan imezda$ nnsent d lĂąuĂ»am"
  11,118,"Lemmer i S ihwi i Mass ik, ad Irr imdanen d yiwen n lois. Zgan mgarraden"
  11,119,"Kkes ed wid i$ef IĂȘun Mass ik. Ixelq iten i wayagi. Itam wawal n Mass ik: \"ad AcaĂŽe$ Loahennama, war ccekk, s leonun akked yimdanen mejmulen"
  11,120,"Ayen akw i k ed NeĂȘka n tmucuha imazanen, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yissent. Id iusan dagi d tidep, d anabi u d asmekti i lmumnin"
  11,121,"Ini i wid ur numin ara: \"xedmet ay tzemrem, nekwni s tidep, la nxeddem"
  11,122,"Gganit, nekwni la nepgani"
  11,123,"N Ăebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. ÂŁuĂŽeS ara u$alen akw lumuĂŽ. Ihi, Ăąabed iT, ppkel fellaS. Ur I$effel ara Mass ik, $ef wayen txeddmem"
  12,1,AlĂŽ. Wigi d issekniyen n Tazmamt ipbegginen
  12,2,"Ih, Nessader it id d LeqwĂŽan, s taĂąĂŽabt, amar a pfehmem"
  12,3,"Nekwni NĂȘekku yak tiĂȘkayin igerzen mavi, deg wayen i k NweĂȘĂȘa di LeqwĂŽan agi, xas telliv, uqbel is, seg wid istehzan"
  12,4,"Mi inna Yusef i baba s: \"a baba! Nek wala$ mrawyan itran, iĂźij, akked waggur, wala$ ten knan iyi"
  12,5,"Inna: \"a mmi! Ur ĂȘekku ayen twalav i watmaten ik, ad ak andin ticeĂŽkep. CciĂźan, s tidep, d acengu n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ n umdan"
  12,6,"Akka, a k Ifren Mass ik, u ak Isselmed asefru n temsal, u ad Itim l$it iS, i keĂ§Ă§ akked twacult n YaĂąqub, akken it Itam, zik, af lejdud ik: IbĂŽahim akked IsĂȘaq. Mass ik, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d UĂ»wib"
  12,7,"Ni$, di Yusef akked watma s, illa ussekni i wid isteqsayen"
  12,8,"Mi nnan: \"war ccekk, ifen a$, Yusef akked gma s, akken iten iĂȘemmel babat nne$, u nekwni d ĂźĂźeĂŽma. Babat nne$, s tidep, haat di ttelfan n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  12,9,"En$et Yusef, ne$ nfut ep si tmurt, a d ilhu degwen babat wen, sinna, a ppu$alem d imdanen ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  12,10,"Inna win d immeslayen, degsen: \"ur neqqet Yusef, veggĂŽet ep ar lqaĂąa n wannu. Ma tgam akka, a t iddem yiwen umsebrid"
  12,11,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, acu k iu$en, ur a$ tuminev ara, $ef Yusef. Nekwni, fellas, s tidep, d unĂ»iĂȘen"
  12,12,"Sseddu t yidne$ azekka, ad izhu, ad iurar. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nĂȘareb fellas"
  12,13,"Inna: \"nek, s tidep, $weble$ ma tebbwim t yidwen, ugade$ a t iĂ§Ă§ lweĂȘc, kunwi testehzam degs"
  12,14,"Nnan: \"ma iĂ§Ă§a t lweĂȘc, u nekwni d ĂźĂźeĂŽma, s tidep a nili d imexsuĂŽen"
  12,15,"Mi t bbwin, mwafaqen a t rĂŽen ar lqaĂąa n wannu, NweĂȘĂȘa yas: \"ad asen temlev, s tidep, lameĂŽ agi nnsen, nitni ur Ă©ĂŽin"
  12,16,"U$alen d tameddit, ar babat sen, pprun"
  12,17,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, s tidep, nĂŽuĂȘ a nemzizzel, neooa Yusef ar lqecc nne$, iĂ§Ă§a t lweĂȘc. Ur a$ teppamnev, xas nenna d tidep"
  12,18,"Bbwin d tasedrit is, degs idamen n rrya. Inna: \"xaĂźi! D iman nnwen i wen d iccacven lameĂŽ. Ilha Ă»Ă»beĂŽ. Anuju $eĂŽ Ăebbi, mgal ayen d teĂȘkam"
  12,19,"Usan d iminigen, uznen win id ippagwmen, issader ssvel is. Inna: \"a lxiĂŽ, wagi d aqcic\"! Ffren t, amzun d sselĂąa. Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa acu xeddmen"
  12,20,"Zzenzen t, s ĂŽĂŽxa, s kra iĂ»uĂŽdiyen. Ur as fkin ara azal"
  12,21,"Inna, i tmeĂźĂźut is, UmaĂ»ĂŽi i t iu$en: \"eĂŽĂȘeb yis, amar ad a$ infaĂą, at nerr d mmit nne$\". Akka ay NesseqĂąad Yusef di tmurt, iwakken ad as NesseĂȘfev asefru n temsal. Ăebbi d Amezwaru s lameĂŽ iS, maca tegwti n medden ur Ă©ĂŽin ara"
  12,22,"Mi d immeĂȘtel, Nefka yas Ă»Ă»wab, tussna. Akka ay Nepkafi iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,23,"Teb$a t tin u$ur izde$. Terra tibbura, u tenna: \"eyya keĂ§Ă§\"! Inna: \"ad iyi Ineooi Ăebbi! Ni$ bab iw iĂŽĂȘeb yissi. S tidep, ur rebĂȘen imednas"
  12,24,"S tidep, teb$a t, u neppa ib$a p, lemmer ur iwala ara atebbet n Mass is. Akka, iwakken a NessebĂąad fellas tuccva, lĂąaĂŽ. Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nneÂŁ izedganen"
  12,25,"Uzzlen ar tebburt, tcerreg as tasedrit is, si zdeffir. Mmugren, argaz is, ar tebburt. Tenna: \"acu ay d aqeĂźĂźi n win iĂąabwlen ad iccmet tawacult ik, siwa lĂȘebs ne$ aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  12,26,"Inna: \"d neppat iyi ib$an\". Icuhhed ed yiwen unagi si twacult is: \"ma teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdat, tenna d tidep, u neppa d akeddab"
  12,27,"Ma teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdeffir, teskaddeb, u neppa seg at tidep"
  12,28,"Mi iwala teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdeffir, inna: \"ayagi, war ccekk, si nncub nnkwent. Ih, nncub nnkwent d timeqwĂŽaĂȘanin"
  12,29,"A Yusef, ppu ayagi, u kem ssuter ssmaĂȘ ubekkav im. Kem, s tidep, teccvev"
  12,30,"La qqaĂŽent tlawin, di temdint: \"tameĂźĂźut umdebbeĂŽ tĂȘemmel acrik is. Teshebl ip tayri. F akken nwala, appan, s tidep, di ttelfan n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  12,31,"Mi tesla s nncub nnsent, tuzen $uĂŽsent, thegga yasent tanalt. I yal yiwet segsent, tefka tafrut. Tenna: \"effe$ ed garasent\". Mi t walant, isdehc itent, jerĂȘent ifassen nnsent, nnant: \"ĂȘaca Ăebbi, wagi maĂ§Ă§i d amdan, wagi siwa d lmelk ukyis"
  12,32,"Tenna: \"d wagi i$ef iyi tlummemt. Ih, b$i$ t, neppa iqqim zeddig. Ma ur ixdim ara ay s umĂŽe$, war ccekk, ad ipwaĂȘbes, ad ipwaĂȘqeĂŽ"
  12,33,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Smenyafe$ lĂȘebs i wayen u$ur iyi d ssawalent. Ma ur TesbaĂądev ara felli nncub nnsent, ad male$ $uĂŽsent, ad ili$ seg wid ur nessin"
  12,34,"Ijaweb as d Mass is. IssebĂąad fellas nncub nnsent. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  12,35,"Sinna, mi ten usan issekniyen, ufan, war ccekk, ilaq a t irr ar lĂȘebs, kra n tallit"
  12,36,"Kecmen yides, ar lĂȘebs, sin ilmeĂ©iyen. Inna yiwen degsen: \"nek wala$ iman iw, la teĂ©Ă©me$ ccĂŽab\". Inna d wayev: \"nek wala$ iman iw, la ppawi$ a$ĂŽum $ef uqeĂŽĂŽu w, la teppen segs ifrax. Ssefru ya$ p id. Ih, nwala k seg iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,37,"Inna: \"seg wayen iyi ss$eĂŽ Mass iw, ad awen p id ssefru$, uqbel a kwen id iawev lqut i wen ppakken. Nek ooi$ ddin n ugdud ur numin s Ăebbi, u nitni nekĂŽen laxeĂŽt"
  12,38,"Ddi$ d ddin n lejdud iw: IbĂŽahim, IsĂȘaq akked YaĂąqub. Ur a$ ippunefk a nezdukkel acemma i Ăebbi. Ayagi si lfevl n Ăebbi fellane$, akw $ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur snemmiren"
  12,39,"A yimeddukwal iw n lĂȘebs, menyif imawlan imfaĂŽaqen, ne$ Ăebbi Yiwen, AqehhaĂŽ"
  12,40,"Ay tĂąabdem, war Neppa, d ismawen kan i sen tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur asen d Issers ara Ăebbi kra udabu. LĂȘukm ar Ăebbi kan. IumeĂŽ ed ur tĂąabdem, siwa Neppa. D wagi ay d ddin uĂ»wib, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  12,41,"A yimeddukwal iw n lĂȘebs, wanag yiwen degwen ad ismiri ccĂŽab, i bab is, wayev ad ippusemmeĂŽ $ef umidag, ifrax ad nneqben aqeĂŽĂŽu s. Ippuseyya lameĂŽ $ef wayen iyi d testeqsam"
  12,42,"Inna i win iĂȘĂ»a ad islek, segsen: \"ar bab ik, smekti iyi d\". CciĂźan iseppu t, ur t id ismekti ar bab is. Irna, di lĂȘebs, kra iseggwasen"
  12,43,"Inna ugellid: \"nek wala$ Ă»a testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent Ă»a tuvĂąifin, akked Ă»a tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquĂŽanin. A yimvebbĂŽen, ssefrut iyi d targit, ma tellam seg wid issefruyen tirga"
  12,44,"Nnan: \"d tirga iwlellsen. Ur nelli d imusnawen i usefru n tirga"
  12,45,"Win i isellken si sin nni, armi tallit id immekti, inna: \"nek, ad awen d awi$ asefru ines, aznet iyi"
  12,46,"A Yusef, bab n tidep, ssefru ya$ d: Ă»a testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent Ă»a tuvĂąifin, akked Ă»a tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquĂŽanin. Amar, ma u$ale$ ar imdanen, amar ad Ă©ĂŽen"
  12,47,"Inna: \"zerĂąat Ă»a iseggwasen imyevfaĂŽen. Ayen tzerĂąam, eooet ep di tyedrin is, siwa cwiĂź ara teĂ§Ă§em"
  12,48,"Sinna, deffir sen, a d asen Ă»a iwaĂąĂŽen. Ad Ă§Ă§en ayen i sen theggam siwa cwiĂź, seg wayen txeznem"
  12,49,"Sinna a d ias, deffir waya, useggwas n tallalt i medden, ideg ara Ă©den"
  12,50,"Inna ugellid: \"awit ep id $uĂŽi\". Mi t id iusa umersul, inna: \"u$al ar bab ik, u steqsi t acu ay d l$eĂŽv n tlawin i ijerĂȘen ifassen nnsent. Mass iw, s tidep, Issen nncub nnsent"
  12,51,"Inna: \"acu ara d tinimt mi teb$amt Yusef\"? Nnant: \"ĂȘaca Ăebbi, ur nufi $uĂŽes tuccva\". Tenna d tmeĂźĂźut umvebbeĂŽ: \"tura, a d tban tidep. D nek i t ib$an, ma d neppa, s tidep, d bab n tidep"
  12,52,"Akka, iwakken ad iĂ©eĂŽ ur t xdiĂąa$ ara s tuffra. Ăebbi ur Inehhu nncub n lxeyyan"
  12,53,"Ur pzekki$ iman iw. Tanefsit, s tidep, tezzu$uĂŽ ar tuccva, siwa ma IĂȘun Mass iw. Mass iw, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  12,54,"Inna ugellid: \"awit ep id $uĂŽi, d laĂątiq iw\". Mi s immeslay, inna: \"keĂ§Ă§, assa, nefka yak adabu, laman"
  12,55,"Inna: \"wekkel iyi $ef lemxazen n tmurt, nek d amĂȘareb amusnaw"
  12,56,"Akka ay NesseqĂąad Yusef di tmurt, ad izde$ anda i s ihwa. NepĂȘunu $ef win i ÂŁ ihwan, ur NesĂŽuĂȘu arraz iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,57,"S tidep, arraz n laxeĂŽt yif it, i wid iumnen u llan pĂȘezziben"
  12,58,"Usan watmaten n Yusef, kecmen $uĂŽes, iĂąqel iten, nitni ur t Ăąqilen"
  12,59,"Mi sen ifka ppĂąabgat nnsen, inna: \"awit iyi d gmat wen s babat wen. Day ur twalam ara zade$ awen lkil, u, nek, ife$ akw wid isnebgaten"
  12,60,"Ma ur iyi t id tebbwim ara, ur awen nepktili $uĂŽi, ur iyi d tepsamim"
  12,61,"Nnan: \"a nĂȘawet baba s fellas; akka ara nexdem"
  12,62,"Inna i iqeddacen is: \"rret selĂąa nnsen deg icekkaĂŽen nnsen, amar a p Ăąaqlen mara awven ar twacult nnsen, amar a d u$alen"
  12,63,"Mi bbwven ar babat sen, nnan: \"a babat nne$, igdel fella$ lkil, azen gmat nne$ yidne$, iwakken a d nektil. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nĂȘareb fellas"
  12,64,"Inna: \"day a kwen amne$ fellas, akken i kwen umne$, zik, $ef gma s? Ăebbi Yif akw imĂȘaraben. Neppa Iphunu sennig akw iĂȘninen"
  12,65,"Mi ldin lqecc nnsen, ufan tu$al iten id selĂąa nnsen. Nnan: \"a babat nne$, ur neb$i tagi, selĂąa nne$ tu$al a$ d. A d nessikrer i twacult nne$, a nĂȘareb $ef gmat nne$, a d nernu ppĂąabga n ul$wem. Tagi d ppĂąabga tushilt"
  12,66,"Inna: \"ur t sedduye$ yidwen, d awez$i, siwa ma tcubkem iyi s Ăebbi, ard a yi t id terrem, siwa ma zzin awen\". Mi s Ăąahden, inna: \"Ăebbi d Awkil $ef wayen id nenna"
  12,67,"Inna: \"a tarwa, ur keĂ§Ă§met si yiwet n tebburt, kecmet si tebbura imgarraden. Ula i wen xedme$, bippa, ar loiha n Ăebbi. AĂȘuddu siwa win n Ăebbi. FellaS ppekle$, fellaS ay ppeklen wid ippkalen"
  12,68,"Mi kecmen akken i sen iumeĂŽ babat sen, ula i sen ixdem, bippa, ar loiha n Ăebbi. D ayen ilezmen kan i iseyya Yaqub, deg iman is. Neppa, s tidep, isĂąa tamusni i s Nesselmed, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  12,69,"Mi kecmen ar Yusef, ibbwi gma s $uĂŽes, inna: \"nekkini d gma k, ur $webbel $ef wayen xeddmen"
  12,70,"Mi sen ifka ppĂąabgat nnsen, irra taqbuct deg ucekkaĂŽ n gma s. Sinna, iberreĂȘ uberraĂȘ: \"a yat terkaf, kunwi, war ccekk, d imakwaren"
  12,71,"Nnan, u zzin $uĂŽsen: \"d acu tesĂŽuĂȘem"
  12,72,"Nnan: \"nesĂŽuĂȘ taqbuct ugellid. Win ip id ibbwin, ad as nefk ppĂąabga n ul$wem. Nek, vemne$ t"
  12,73,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi, nni$ teĂ©ĂŽam ur d nusa ara a nessefsed tamurt, ur nelli d imakwaren"
  12,74,"Nnan: \"d acu ay d aqeĂźĂźi s, ma teskadbem"
  12,75,"Nnan: \" aqeĂźĂźi n win i p ibbwin di tcekkaĂŽt is, d yiman is. Akka ay nepkafi imednas"
  12,76,"Ibda la ipqellib icekkaĂŽen, uqbel win n gma s, sinna, issuffe$ ip id seg ucekkaĂŽ n gma s. Akka ay Nefka ticeĂŽkep i Yusef. Ur izmir ad iĂźĂźef gma s, s lqanun ugellid, siwa ma Irad Ăebbi. Nessalay, tiseddaĂŽin, win i ÂŁihwan. Sennig bu tussna, illa Umusnaw"
  12,77,"Nnan: \"ma iuker, ni$ iuker, zik, yiwen n watma s\". Iffer ip Yusef $uĂŽes, ur asen p id inna ara. Inna: \"aql akwen deg yir ĂȘala. Ăebbi Yif akw akken IĂ©ĂŽa ayen d teqqaĂŽem"
  12,78,"Nnan: \"a yameqwĂŽan, baba s, s tidep, wesser. EĂźĂźef yiwen segne$ deg umekkan is. Nwala k, ih, telliv si lĂąuĂ»am"
  12,79,"Inna: \"ur a$ IĂąammed Ăebbi a neĂźĂźef, siwa win u$uĂŽ nufa ta$awsa nne$. Mulac, war ccekk, a nili d imednas"
  12,80,"Mi uysen segs, mcawaĂŽen, inna umeqwĂŽan segsen: \"day ur teĂ©ĂŽim ara, ar babat wen tcubkem t s Ăebbi, u, zik, tveggĂąam Yusef? Ihi, ur pĂŽuĂȘu$ si tmurt a, d awez$i, alamma iserreĂȘ iyi baba, ne$ Ifra Ăebbi felli. Neppa, Yif akw imĂȘaddan"
  12,81,"U$alet ar babat wen, tinem as: a babat nne$, mmi k, s tidep, iuker. Ncehhed kan $ef wayen neĂ©ĂŽa, ur nessawev i tbavnit"
  12,82,"Steqsi tamdint ideg i nella, akked terkift ukud nedda. Ih, d tidep, ay d nenna"
  12,83,"Inna: \"xaĂźi! LameĂŽ seg iman nnwen. Ilha Ă»Ă»beĂŽ. Amar Ăebbi a yi ten id Iawi akw. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, d Amusnaw"
  12,84,"Ijuneb iten, u inna: \"a lĂȘif iw $ef Yusef\"! Allen is ijegger itent u$ilif, innu$ben"
  12,85,"Nnan: \"s Ăebbi, tezgiv tesmektayev d Yusef, alamma tu$alev d amuvin, ne$ seg wid immuten"
  12,86,"Inna: \"la pcetki$ kan i Ăebbi, s uneĂ©mi w akked u$wbel iw. Ssne$, s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  12,87,"A yarraw iw, ĂŽuĂȘet, steqsit $ef Yusef akked gma s. Ur ppayset di tecvaĂź n Ăebbi. Ih, i ippaysen di tecvaĂź n Ăebbi, siwa agdud ijehliyen"
