  14,44,"Nabi imdanen af wass ideg ara ten id yas uĂąaqeb. Ad inin wid idensen: \"a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ lmudda wezzilen, a d njaweb i unabi K, a neddu d imazanen\". \"Day ur teggulem ara kunwi, zik, ar ur tep$abem"
