  15,99,"AĂąbed Mass ik, ar k id ias utebbet"
  16,1,"Ad ias lameĂŽ n Ăebbi, ur pĂȘirit $uĂŽes. Gedha s yiS! Ay AĂąlay, sennig wayen pcaraken"
  16,2,"Issrusu d lmalayek s ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ si lameĂŽ iS, $ef win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS: \"NedĂŽet ar ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, ĂȘezzbet iyI"
  16,3,"Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ay AĂąlay sennig wayen pcaraken"
  16,4,"Ixelq ed amdan si tiqqit; atan iu$al aS, d axĂ»im n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  16,5,"Ixelq awen d lmal, segsen iceĂźĂźiven iĂȘman, aba$uĂŽ, u, segsen, teppeppem"
  16,6,"D ccbaĂȘa nnwen mara ten id terrem, u mara ten teksem"
  16,7,"Ppawin tiĂąkkwmin nnwen ar tmurt ur teppawvem, siwa ma tĂąapbem. Ih, Mass nnwen, war ccekk, d UmĂąin, d AĂȘnin"
  16,8,"IĂąewdiwen, iserdyan, i$wyal, i rrekba nnwen akked ccbaĂȘa. Ixelleq ayen ur tessinem"
  16,9,"D Ăebbi i Ippawin d ubrid. Ff$en segs. Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Inhu meĂŽĂŽa"
  16,10,"D Neppa i wen d Isse$layen aman seg igenni. Segsen tissit nnwen, segsen ttjuĂŽ i itepp lmal"
  16,11,"Isskar awen d yissen nnaĂąma, azemmur, tizdayin, tiĂ©uĂŽin, akked yal ppemĂŽa. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ipxemmimen"
  16,12,"Inub awen d s yiv akked wass, iĂźij akked waggur. Itran ppemnuben s lameĂŽ iS. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen"
  16,13,"I wen d Ixleq di tmurt, degs initen imgarraden. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ismektayen"
  16,14,"D Neppa i Inuben s yill, iwakken a pteppem, segs, aksum aleqqaq, a d teksem, segs, rrĂȘuĂȘ i teppeqqnem. A pwaliv lbabuĂŽ ipcerrig it, iwakken a pnadim si lfevl iS, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  16,15,"Issers idurar $ef tmurt, ur teppembwiwil yiswen; isaffen, iberdan, amar a ppepwanham"
  16,16,"timuliwin: s yitran, nitni pwanhan"
  16,17,Day Win Ixelqen am win ur nxelleq? Day ur d tesmektayem ara
  16,18,"Lemmer a pĂȘesbem l$it n Ăebbi, ur tezmirem. Ih, Ăebbi, war ccekk, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  16,19,Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa ayen teffrem akked wayen teqqaĂŽem
  16,20,"Wid u$uĂŽ pnujun, war Ăebbi, ur illi wayen xelqen. D nitni i ipwaxelqen"
  16,21,"D lmeggtin ur d imuddiren, ur Ă©ĂŽin melmi ara ten id ssekren"
  16,22,"Ăebbi nnwen d Ăebbi Yiwen. Wid ur numin ara s laxeĂŽt, d ulawen nnsen i iugin. U nitni pzzuxun"
  16,23,"War ccekk, Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaĂŽen. Neppa, s tidep, ur IĂȘemmel ara imzuxiyen"
  16,24,"Ma nnan asen: \"d acu id Issers Mass nnwen\"? QqaĂŽen: \"d timucuha imezwura"
  16,25,"Ad bibben, ass n tnekra, tiĂąakkwmin nnsen, s pmam nnsent, akked wumur si tĂąakkwmin n wid telfen, mebla ma faqen. Day maĂ§Ă§i dir it wayen bubben"
  16,26,"Ih, undin p, wid i ten id izwaren. Ăebbi IaĂątad lebni nnsen, si llsas. I$li d ssqef fellasen. Iusa ten id uĂąaqeb seg wanda ur bnin"
  16,27,"Sinna, ass n tnekra, a ten Idull, ad Yini: \"anda ten icriken iW, i$ef temnamarem\"? Nnan imawlan n tussna: \"war ccekk, ddell akked ddens, assa, $ef ijehliyen"
  16,28,"iwumi ddment lmalayek leĂŽwaĂȘ, nitni densen iman nnsen\". A d ssutren tifrat: \"ur nexdim kra n tucmip\". XaĂźi, Ăebbi, s tidep, IĂ©ĂŽa ayen txeddmem"
  16,29,"Kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama; degs a pwekkĂŽem. A yicmet uxxam imzuxiyen"
  16,30,"Ad inin i wid ipĂȘezziben: \"d acu id Issers Mass nnwen\"? A d inin: \"d lxiĂŽ\". I wid imaĂąnen, ise$ di ddunit agi. PifxiĂŽ, war ccekk, axxam aneggaru. Ay d umĂąin uxxam n wid ipĂȘezziben"
  16,31,"Ad kecmen leonanat n Ăaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen; degsen, i nitni, ayen i sen ihwan. Akka i Ipkafi Ăebbi wid ipĂȘezziben"
  16,32,"wid iwumi ddment lmalayek leĂŽwaĂȘ, nitni maĂąnen, ad asen inint: \"tifrat fellawen! Kecmet Loennet, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  16,33,"Day a pĂŽaoun kan tisin n lmalayek $uĂŽsen, ne$ a d iawev lameĂŽ n Mass ik? Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Ur ten Idnis Ăebbi, maca densen iman nnsen"
  16,34,"D tucmitin xeddmen, i ten iwwten. Izzi yasen wayen i$ef pmmaĂąliken"
  16,35,"Nnan wid ipcaraken: \"Lemmer i S ihwi i Ăebbi, ur naĂąbed acemma, war Neppa, nekwni akked imezwura nne$. Ur negdel acemma, war ayen Igdel\". Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Day illa wayen iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen"
  16,36,"Ni$ Nuzen ed amazan i yal lois: \"Ăąabdet Ăebbi, janbet iĂŽebbiten n tkerkas\". Garasen, llan wid Inha Ăebbi; garasen, wid i$ef iura ttelfan. Iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevĂŽa d inekkaĂŽen"
  16,37,"Xas tĂŽe$wbev $ef nnhaya nnsen, Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu wid Itlef. Ur asen illi usettaĂŽ"
  16,38,"Ggulen s Ăebbi, liman iĂ»eĂȘĂȘan nnsen, ar ur d Ippara ara Ăebbi wid immuten. XaĂźi, lemĂąahda fellas d tidep, maca tegwti n medden ur ssinen"
  16,39,"Iwakken ad asen d ibeggen ayen i$ef mgarraden, iwakken ad Ă©ĂŽen wid ijehlen, ar nitni, war ccekk, llan d ikeddaben"
  16,40,"Awal nneÂŁ kan, i t$awsa, ma Neb$a p, ad as Nini: \"ili\"! A ppili"
  16,41,"Wid iunagen i Ăebbi, mbaĂąd ma pwadensen, a ten Nesserked di ddunit s yise$. Arraz n laxeĂŽt a t i$leb, war ccekk, lemmer Ă©ĂŽin"
  16,42,wid iĂ»ebĂŽen u ppeklen $ef Mass nnsen
  16,43,"Id Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen iwumi NweĂȘĂȘa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teĂ©ĂŽim ara"
  16,44,"S ubeggen akked Ihellilen, Nuzen ak d asmekti, iwakken a pbeggnev i medden, ayen i sen d irsen, amar a d mmektin"
  16,45,"Wid iundin tucmitin, aĂąni $ilen ur IĂŽemmu ara Ăebbi di tmurt, ne$ ur ten id ippawev ara uĂąaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin"
  16,46,"Ne$ ur ten id ikkat ara di cce$l nnsen, ur sfunnugen"
